    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-primary">Indian Food Catering Services</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted">Make your events memorable with the best Indian food catering in Charlotte, NC.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
